                <h1>Shein: Unraveling Its Origins and Global Reach</h1>
                <p>Shein is a global online retailer headquartered in Nanjing, China. Founded in 2008, it initially focused on selling women's clothing but has since expanded to include men's, children's apparel, accessories, and home goods. Shein is known for its fast-fashion models, leveraging trendy designs and quick production times to cater to a global audience.</p>
